---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Contact Me"
	description="Get in touch with Astro Tobby"
	pubDate={new Date('May 27 2026')}
	image="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		Have questions, suggestions, or just want to say hello? I'd love to hear from you. You can reach out to me through the following channels:
	</p>

	<h3>Email</h3>
	<p>
		For direct inquiries, please email me at: <a href="mailto:tobby@astrotobby.site">tobby@astrotobby.site</a>
	</p>

	<h3>Social Media</h3>
	<p>
		Stay updated and connect with me on social media:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Twitter/X:</strong> <a href="https://twitter.com/astrotobby" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@astrotobby</a></li>
		<li><strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/astrotobby" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">astrotobby</a></li>
	</ul>

	<p>
		I'll do my best to get back to you as soon as possible. Thank you for your interest in my blog!
	</p>
</Layout>
